{"tid":1470633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地一直都冇輸過，只係未夠完美！","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:14:22.000Z","uid":27387,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e429a8d3feb6148bf5cb402512390ea5e19a66","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"我唔係想代表邊個或者出黎佔道德高地，但經過呢兩日機場一事，我覺得好多手足忘記左啲嘢......<br />\n<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一，尋晚彈左堆話出機場道歉嘅post，好快樓下嘅意見就兩極化。其實手足各自爬山，唔需要分咁細，一個運動總有不同意見嘅人，試下唔好屌，試下同人講加油，咁先係唔分化，同埋對準政權，呢個仆街政府先我地嘅目標，唔係遊客。<br />\n<br />\n第二，捉到有鬼唔洗急住幫佢開年，搭下膊頭合下照拍下片，千其唔好唔小心除左佢口罩，或者好唔小咁kick低佢。大家學下咁<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=hUrfQ4juy3Y&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhUrfQ4juy3Y%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=b4f8403f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=hUrfQ4juy3Y&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>，盡量減少痛腳俾人捉。<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>綁起拉埋一二邊做咩冇人知，可能佢跣親呢......</del></span><br />\n<br />\n第三，冇底線唔代表冇良知，知道大家都好躁好想攞popo黎開年，但係要記住「與怪物戰鬥的人 應當小心自己不要成為怪物。當你長久凝視深淵時 深淵也在凝視你。」有鬼上左白車就唔好追打，追住佢去醫院好過，等大家知佢去向仲好，記者救護嘅身份同行事係絕對中立，有嘢就報，有人就救，我地唔係狗。<br />\n<br />\n第四，唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦，唔好成為怪獸，機場本應該係一個和理非嘅行動，所以我地要忍，向內外大大力輸出革命，唔俾人走又點會輸出，取唔取消唔係靠硬，係靠人數，812係最理想嘅結果，所以話「永遠都差啲嘢，就係差你一個」，只要等到popo忍唔到出手先，到時就係我地嘅贏利，要緊記天琦講過嘅嘢在心中。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日真係好撚心痛，有義士s俾狗拉左，有義士冇左隻眼，更心痛嘅係大家內部開始出現分歧，太有當年嘅影子.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地唔可以俾成個運動無疾而終，只有贏先有出路，我地呢一刻要做嘅嘢係更加團結，歷史係用黎做前車之鑑，唔好俾敵人分化我地，只有實現5大訴求先係唯一出路！</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟咁耐以黎第一次開post，只希望大家睇得入眼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a40a13b102963a640b4dd954a4c142ff2ed8b4a7","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連 1/10"},{"pid":"4b82befca26d29b2a3853cc955869c0097ecf30d","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"自推十連 2/10"},{"pid":"476e21083b9978bc7bfa425dae39ba81d86ea312","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連 3/10"},{"pid":"931fd4741b826cb7af40e7f7e71bcd23e8d114f8","tid":1470633,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"816 818"},{"pid":"b6d36714d973193836885d36acd7dea24aedc81e","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 4/10"},{"pid":"2a6c2a96f23f28e53710147b055e2b8f3b6f9efa","tid":1470633,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0ea4f2623a473aab0532f4d6c9ef0fe457ec99d","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連 5/10"},{"pid":"b1d3a3282ca8628df25f8ad85871bae9184fba70","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連 6/10"},{"pid":"83b8140228b61a9c6e7622c7d5d1f8a0d7448ce1","tid":1470633,"uid":164340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"其實善忘既香港人可以堅持到今時今刻已經無輸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ee073c79213a8116efe8b169a0f654e4ff8119","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"自推十連 7/10"},{"pid":"3d5271b36f662b3fe31415a5819c60c51b2b7485","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連 8/10"},{"pid":"fa94877bdcc1c776dd48a36f08387b2ec6c64650","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 9/10"},{"pid":"e4ca825e0edb243cc0da7631dfba9f42d1e7f00c","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:11:17.000Z","msg":"自推十連 10/10"},{"pid":"6ce923dfdda7484bbb1fd16310cb1b5b9b06e4e5","tid":1470633,"uid":34253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"我哋係人，總會有做錯決定嘅時候，汲取經驗，下次做好咪得囉"},{"pid":"8dbb55a6a2e9e829b011a9ea46456eac8e8cf91f","tid":1470633,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣做野啦</span></span><br />\n香港人咁善忘？！依幾單野無人提啦？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469440</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25be3b057e932b795f4ec3efac4fb984ad2a2037","tid":1470633,"uid":128995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"有做得唔好既地方可以大家討論/批判，但請不要指責。我地目標都係一致，有事一齊咩好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0523dc7563197dfef89a2e0c2b6f1c07ad197d6e","tid":1470633,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"有禮貌問佢影咩撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人精神咁先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我對攝影好有研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢句笑左"},{"pid":"46c9069eb65dc7510bb04813e31a020f8dba17e2","tid":1470633,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25b074c99a25b47661457a846c069a23f962930d","tid":1470633,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"79c4cb2136e6ef47aa3fcb41c3e638dd453ccd30","tid":1470633,"uid":27387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人誰無過錯</span><br />\n<br />\n大家要攬住個初心，一齊向住目標一齊行<br />\n<br />\n不論係手足定五大訴求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n可以我懇請各位手足唔好再互屌，一齊行"},{"pid":"b01289234cbf1b0172367b03dfa7a1287726781e","tid":1470633,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其<strong>象徵意義</strong>。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"}]}